3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI techniques to automate the network design process and optimize the iris network. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper discusses the optimality of the classic IrisCode, which is a cryptographic technique used in iris recognition.
